data.title: 3 bedroom apartment for sale in Rodin Piano Nobile, France, France
data.meta_description: A stone's throw from the Rodin Museum and the Matignon Hotel, located at a remarkable and highly prized address in the 7th arrondissement, on the noble floor, accessible by lift, from an old mansion, exceptional apartment of 207 m² on the ground (188 m² Carrez law).
